{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unbound Drift is a high acceleration physics game built around the desire for speed and the grace of elastic motion. Once you've mastered the simplistic controls you'll be soaring through space at nerve inducing speeds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339860/extras/BigGif_FastSmash.gif?t=1737588962\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Physics Driven Mastery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Behind the simple swings and artful arcs lies tons of physics fun. Every obstacle is an opportunity to bounce, every corner an opportunity to wrap yourself around. At high speeds, even your tether is loaded with elasticity, allowing you to slingshot yourself to the stars!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339860/extras/PerfectS.gif?t=1737588962\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You Are Speed!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reaching max speed in the game is a feat. Maintaining that speed even more so.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try not to get distracted by the elusive golden trail as you dash to avoid obstacles and whip yourself around the asteroids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339860/extras/GottaGoFast.gif?t=1737588962\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Unmarked High</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kick back and enjoy the peaceful Zen asteroid field. No timers, no pressure, just a place for you to relax and show off your mastery amongst the space rocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339860/extras/ZenAsteroids.gif?t=1737588962\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3339860?t=173758